  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BestGuessPresTableModel
    A table model decorator that uses FirstRowRotationTableModel if the result set has only one row and the delegate otherwise.
    CachedRSTableModel
    Stores row data in memory as a table model.
    CachedTableModel
    Stores row data in memory as a table model.
    FirstRowRotationTableModel
    A table model decorator (pattern) that gives the column names in one column and the data in another column for cases where there is only one row.
    PackingColumnWidthJTable
    A table GUI component that adjusts each column to show as much data as possible in the narrowest width possible column.
    ResultSetFrame
    A frame that contains a ResultSetPanel.
    ResultSetPanel
    A GUI panel that displays data from an ResultSet instance.
    ResultsFrame
    Create a frame to display results using data as a list of lists, optionally with columns.
    ScrollableRSTableModel
    A table model that models a ResultSet of data.
